steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
Debug step:
When I navigate to menu "Mobile app" with submenu "Mobile Editor"
Then I should see Mobile screen display
When I select tab name Pages with index 1
When I add new screen with name JIT039OTPPreviewCode
Then I should see the screen with name JIT039OTPPreviewCode display in list Pages
When I select screen with name JIT039OTPPreviewCode
When I select tab list with name "Layers"
When I open Search popup on item value "JIT039OTPPreviewCode" with index "1"
When I add item "OTPInput" in Search popup with sub menu "Form" to preview mobile editor
When I open preview code with component mode
Then I should see the code content "M39a_MAIN_OTP_INIT"
When I close preview code panel
When I toggle on item value "JIT039OTPPreviewCode" with index "1"
When I select item value "OTPInput" with index "1"
When I toggle off Layout tree header
When I select dropdown field label "OTP Input Type" of header "Container" with value "box"
When I sleep 1
When I select the color for field label "Background Color" of header "Container" by inputting the hexcode value "#FF0000"
When I update field label "Pin Count" of header "Keyboard" with value "4"
When I select dropdown field label "Keyboard Type" of header "Keyboard" with value "Number"
When I select checkbox with label "Auto Focus" of header "Keyboard"
When I update field label "Width" of header "Cell Style" with value "70"
When I select the color for field label "Background Color" of header "Cell Style" by inputting the hexcode value "#FF0000"
When I update field label "Height" of header "Cell Style" with value "70"
When I select the color for field label "Border Color" of header "Cell Style" by inputting the hexcode value "#0007FF"
When I select dropdown field label "Border Style" of header "Cell Style" with value "solid"
When I update field label "Radius" of header "Cell Style" with radio "PX" and value "20"
When I update field label "Border Width" of header "Cell Style" with value "10"
When I select dropdown field label "Font Family" of header "Cell Text" with value "Default"
When I select dropdown field label "Font Weight" of header "Cell Text" with value "bold"
When I update field label "Size" of header "Cell Text" with value "20"
When I select field label "Text Align" of header "Cell Text" with radio icon has attribute aria-label "align-center"
When I update field label "Line Height" of header "Cell Text" with value "18"
When I select the color for field label "Color" of header "Cell Text" by inputting the hexcode value "#FF0000"
When I update field label "Letter Spacing" of header "Cell Text" with value "2"
When I turn on the toggle button label "Letter Spacing" of header "Cell Text" with value "italic"
When I turn on the toggle button label "Letter Spacing" of header "Cell Text" with value "underline"
When I update margin-padding id "marginTop" of header "Spacing" with value "10"
When I update margin-padding id "marginLeft" of header "Spacing" with value "10"
When I update margin-padding id "marginBottom" of header "Spacing" with value "10"
When I update margin-padding id "marginRight" of header "Spacing" with value "10"
When I update margin-padding id "paddingTop" of header "Spacing" with value "10"
When I update margin-padding id "paddingLeft" of header "Spacing" with value "10"
When I update margin-padding id "paddingBottom" of header "Spacing" with value "10"
When I update margin-padding id "paddingRight" of header "Spacing" with value "10"
When I open preview code with style mode
Then I should see the code content "M39a_STYLE_OTP"
